         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Hobart Town ¶ 9th April 1866 ¶ Dear Sir, ¶  ¶ I duly received your letter in reference to Mons. Ramel's discovery &amp; at once searched our list of Patents none of which mention the use of Eucalyptus lea...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">66.04.09</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Morton Allport</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Letter press copy book, Allport Library and Museum of Fine Arts, Hobart.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Hobart Town</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">9th April 1866</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I duly received your letter in reference to Mons. Ramel's discovery &amp; at once searched our list of Patents none of which mention the use of Eucalyptus leaves —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Though I shall be happy to aid you in obtaining a patent here the agency you speak of would be quite out of my way of business. A friend of mine Mr Lavington Roope a well known and highly respected Hobart Town Merchant will however gladly accept the agency on the ordinary terms —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In order to obtain the patent you had better lose no time in sending over to me the necessary specifications &amp;c</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I will take care to enter a caveat against the application of any other person to obtain a Patent for M. Ramel's invention till I again hear from you —</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">I remain</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yours sincerely</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Morton Allport<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">this needs following up in Patent records, presumably in Hobart.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Prof. F. Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanical Gardens</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
